title: Photos: Blue Jays topple Rangers in epic Game 5 playoff decider
text:
Toronto Blue Jays Jose Bautista (left) celebrates his three-run homer with teammates Ryan Goins (right) and Josh Donaldson during the seventh inning in Game 5 of their American League Division Series at Rogers Centre in Toronto on Wednesday, Oct. 14, 2015. The Blue Jays won 6-3 to advance to the American League Championship Series. Photograph by: Nathan Denette , The Canadian Press 
The Toronto Blue Jays and the Texas Rangers go at it in the fifth and deciding game of their American League Divisional Series at Rogers Centre in Toronto, a remarkable clash capped by Jose Bautista’s seventh-inning, three-run homer to lift the Jays to a 6-3 victory. © Copyright (c) The Vancouver Sun
